Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.41,0:01:43.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Carpe diem.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.04,0:01:45.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}If I miss this chance,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.29,0:01:49.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}it may never bless me again.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.80,0:01:53.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}So I must seize the day while it lasts.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.30,0:01:59.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I have to seize each day\Nso I can live without regrets!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.56,0:02:03.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah! That's what I'm gonna do!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.39,0:02:08.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}"Carpe diem"{\i0}\Nis my new life's motto!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.73,0:02:11.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Carpe diem!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.78,0:02:18.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.74,0:02:21.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, hey Moon!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.20,0:02:21.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.58,0:02:24.37,Default,,0,0,0,,James!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.37,0:02:28.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Aah, I'm so, so happy we met, James!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.59,0:02:30.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.76,0:02:37.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to seize this encounter with you\Nwhile it lasts. As they say, {\i1}carpe diem!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.05,0:02:40.64,Default,,0,0,0,,O-Okay. Not sure what that means,\Nbut come on in.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.64,0:02:43.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I just got a new video game\Nif you wanna play.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.60,0:02:48.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Here I come! Take that!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.52,0:02:48.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}You won't beat me that easily!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.90,0:02:51.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Enjoying the game?\NYou sure look like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.07,0:02:56.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Is there something on my face?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.57,0:03:02.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, no. It just hit me, I've never seen the face\Nyou make when you're focused on a game before!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.33,0:03:03.33,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.33,0:03:07.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Come to think of it, I don't think I've\N{\i1}ever{\i0} stared at you up close before!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.04,0:03:09.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I... {\i1}really{\i0} don't like being stared at.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.88,0:03:11.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you overlook it please?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.13,0:03:13.51,Default,,0,0,0,,O-Oh right!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.51,0:03:16.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I could go for a bath!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.01,0:03:17.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay! I'll wait here!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.39,0:03:22.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't! I'm very meticulous,\Nso I'll be in there for ages!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.47,0:03:26.94,Default,,0,0,0,,You can just head out when you're done\Nwith the game, alright? {\i1}Au revoir !
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.40,0:03:33.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Man. Something's off about him today.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.86,0:03:40.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Want some help washing\Nyour back?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.20,0:03:44.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Aagh! What the heck? {\i1}Non merci,{\i0} please!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.79,0:03:45.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}No need to be shy.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.54,0:03:49.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}We're both guys, so you have\Nnothing to be worried about.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.50,0:03:52.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Get out of here!!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.26,0:03:55.97,Default,,0,0,0,,What's your problem?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.38,0:04:02.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, but can you blame me?\NYou can't just walk in on me like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.26,0:04:05.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry — I'm making an exquisite dish\Nthat'll turn your mood around!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.10,0:04:09.35,Default,,0,0,0,,You should've said so sooner!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.77,0:04:13.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll help you cook! Oh-ho-ho!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.82,0:04:15.57,Default,,0,0,0,,You really don't have to!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.57,0:04:17.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Then I'll stay here and watch!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.07,0:04:24.62,Default,,0,0,0,,It's ready! James-style Italian pasta!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.62,0:04:27.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I added lots of cilantro for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.75,0:04:29.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, you want some cheese?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.88,0:04:33.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Shoot! I forgot Moon hates cilantro!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.96,0:04:35.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry! I can make you a new one!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.51,0:04:42.05,Default,,0,0,0,,This is so good! Ulp!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.05,0:04:43.55,Default,,0,0,0,,A-Are you sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.55,0:04:46.97,Default,,0,0,0,,You went out of your way\Nto make me this!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.97,0:04:49.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't complain about it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.19,0:04:51.10,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't {\i1}have{\i0} to eat it...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.10,0:04:53.40,Default,,0,0,0,,But I have to seize this moment too!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.40,0:04:56.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I may never meet this cilantro again!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.03,0:05:00.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Unbelievable...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.37,0:05:03.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, James!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.45,0:05:07.37,Default,,0,0,0,,That tasted amazing!\NI'll never forget it as long as I live!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.87,0:05:12.83,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a little dramatic...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.00,0:05:15.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you home, Cony?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.63,0:05:20.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Moon! Check this out!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.26,0:05:21.88,Default,,0,0,0,,This just came in.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.88,0:05:26.39,Default,,0,0,0,,It trains your inner muscles.\NIt's supposed to help you lose weight!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.39,0:05:29.14,Default,,0,0,0,,One, two! One, two!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.14,0:05:32.73,Default,,0,0,0,,What's with the stare-down?\NDo you wanna give it a try?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.73,0:05:33.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.65,0:05:35.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.90,0:05:40.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Ack! What just happened?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.15,0:05:42.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't spread your legs so wide!\NClose them!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.66,0:05:52.96,Default,,0,0,0,,That's hilarious.\NYou're such a ditz, Moon!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.00,0:05:55.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Cony...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.50,0:05:59.05,Default,,0,0,0,,You mad? You know I'm right... Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.05,0:06:01.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks for that. It was real fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.47,0:06:04.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, what's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.22,0:06:06.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing. I'm just fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.80,0:06:10.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I see. You scared me for a sec.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.89,0:06:14.10,Default,,0,0,0,,All this exercise is making me thirsty!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.10,0:06:16.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you get me something to drink?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.27,0:06:20.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Here you go! It's calorie-free!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.69,0:06:23.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?! Normally you would've gotten mad at me...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.91,0:06:27.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you sure you're alright?\NMaybe you have a fever.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.83,0:06:31.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I must seize this day\Nwhile it lasts! {\i1}Carpe diem!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.41,0:06:33.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, parfait what now?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.75,0:06:37.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Ugh, thanks for that.\NNow I'm craving a strawberry parfait!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.50,0:06:39.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Wanna come with?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.00,0:06:41.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Alas, I'm running out of time.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.21,0:06:42.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Goodbye!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.22,0:06:46.18,Default,,0,0,0,,What was that about?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.97,0:06:52.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Ouch, that smarts...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.10,0:06:55.23,Default,,0,0,0,,What's a rock doing here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.23,0:06:56.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Why, you...!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.03,0:07:04.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Brown, I didn't see you there!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.11,0:07:06.16,Default,,0,0,0,,You were taking a nap?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.53,0:07:09.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Talk about a real chance encounter!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.49,0:07:14.87,Default,,0,0,0,,If I hadn't tripped here,\NI would'a walked right past you!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.87,0:07:16.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Ain't that something, Brown?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.67,0:07:19.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so glad we met! Whoo!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.46,0:07:20.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold up!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.92,0:07:24.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't forget about the rock.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.17,0:07:27.34,Default,,0,0,0,,If I hadn't met this,\NI wouldn't have met you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.51,0:07:32.52,Default,,0,0,0,,This really is its own special encounter!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.52,0:07:36.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Brown!\NYou too, little rock!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.27,0:07:37.60,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll meet again!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.60,0:07:39.52,Default,,0,0,0,,See you!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.32,0:07:46.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.86,0:07:49.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Watch where you're going!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.45,0:07:50.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.62,0:07:54.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hold on. This, too, is an encounter...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.04,0:07:56.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you hurt, good sir?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.71,0:07:57.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.42,0:08:00.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Our meeting is no happenstance.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.08,0:08:03.42,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a miracle on our planet,\Nnay, in this galaxy!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.42,0:08:04.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.38,0:08:10.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh? Is that Moon?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.51,0:08:17.85,Default,,0,0,0,,The chance of the Siding Spring comet\Ncolliding with Mars is 1/250,000.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.85,0:08:23.86,Default,,0,0,0,,And a meteorite large enough to wipe out the dinosaurs\Nonly hit Earth once in 100 million years.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.36,0:08:29.32,Default,,0,0,0,,It's possible those are the same odds\Nthat we would run into each other today,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.86,0:08:33.33,Default,,0,0,0,,making this nothing short of a miracle.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.16,0:08:34.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I see?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.66,0:08:41.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Really? I wonder what's gotten into him.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.88,0:08:45.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Something is up with him.\NI just know it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.01,0:08:51.55,Default,,0,0,0,,He said some weird stuff to me earlier.\NLike "I won't forget this as long as I live."
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.55,0:08:54.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh yeah. He told me he was\N"running out of time."
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.39,0:08:58.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? He told you "we'll meet again?"
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.60,0:09:04.36,Default,,0,0,0,,What's going on?\NHe's acting like he's leaving us for good.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.36,0:09:06.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe he is.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.07,0:09:12.36,Default,,0,0,0,,It sounds a lot like he is\Nsaying farewell to you all.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.36,0:09:14.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Farewell?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.53,0:09:18.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. He must be leaving Line Town soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.41,0:09:23.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Aah, how could you, Moon?!\NWhy wouldn't you tell us directly?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.71,0:09:28.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe he was so sad\Nhe couldn't get himself to.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.93,0:09:36.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Phew. I feel like I really seized the day.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.23,0:09:42.69,Default,,0,0,0,,It's from James.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.52,0:09:48.73,Default,,0,0,0,,"I'm holding a party tonight.\NCome on down, we're all waiting."
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.73,0:09:50.19,Default,,0,0,0,,A party?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.99,0:09:53.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Come in!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.53,0:09:55.37,Default,,0,0,0,,What the?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.37,0:09:58.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Juby-julee! The special guest has arrived!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.37,0:09:59.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.12,0:10:02.29,Default,,0,0,0,,What took you so long, Moon?\NWe were getting tired!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.29,0:10:04.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, this way!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.17,0:10:05.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Here!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.04,0:10:09.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-What kind of party is this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.80,0:10:13.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry about it.\NHave some juice!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.01,0:10:14.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Cheers!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.76,0:10:15.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.72,0:10:17.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.72,0:10:23.19,Default,,0,0,0,,This is a present from me to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.19,0:10:24.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Say what?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.27,0:10:26.19,Default,,0,0,0,,This one's from me!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.19,0:10:28.15,Default,,0,0,0,,This is from the both of us!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.57,0:10:36.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, hold on. I didn't get you guys anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.12,0:10:39.99,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a farewell party.\NYou don't need to give us anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.99,0:10:41.66,Default,,0,0,0,,A farewell party?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.66,0:10:43.46,Default,,0,0,0,,For who?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.54,0:10:45.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.21,0:10:47.21,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.92,0:10:52.38,Default,,0,0,0,,What?! It's for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.67,0:10:55.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry I didn't notice, Moon...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.30,0:10:59.31,Default,,0,0,0,,It didn't occur to me you had come\Nto say goodbye earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.64,0:11:03.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Please don't forget about us, Moon.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.23,0:11:06.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Kn-Knock it off already!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.98,0:11:12.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I see. So you were just inspired by a movie.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.36,0:11:16.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks for misleading us, dude.\NYou better give back your presents!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.24,0:11:18.70,Default,,0,0,0,,You misled yourselves!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.70,0:11:22.91,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a pretty normal takeaway\Nfrom your weird behavior.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.91,0:11:25.16,Default,,0,0,0,,But I'm glad you're staying for real.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.16,0:11:29.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course I am.\NWhere am I supposed to go?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.04,0:11:31.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I made strawberry parfaits!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.17,0:11:32.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.09,0:11:36.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Yum!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.05,0:11:39.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Carpe{\i0} is overrated—parfaits are where it's at!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.31,0:11:44.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Same here!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.64,0:11:48.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hi-yah!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.48,0:11:51.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah! That's what I'm gonna do!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.61,0:11:55.78,Default,,0,0,0,,"Don't think, feel"\Nis my new life's motto!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.11,0:11:59.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi-{\i1}yah!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.75,0:12:10.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}This man is the star\Nof tonight's special.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.83,0:12:13.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}He spotted the blue butterfly,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.88,0:12:17.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}a rare specimen said for generations\Nto bring happiness to people.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.55,0:12:23.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Since then, happiness and success\Nhave blessed him many times,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.89,0:12:28.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}earning him the name\Nof the happiest man in Line Town.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.10,0:12:31.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Perhaps you will be the next person
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.36,0:12:34.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}to be graced by the blue butterfly!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.40,0:12:37.19,Default,,0,0,0,,That was a nice special!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.19,0:12:40.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I gotta find that blue butterfly!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.70,0:12:45.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Blue butterfly, oh blue butterfly...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.91,0:12:49.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh blue butterfly!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.83,0:12:53.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, hi Cony! I take it you saw\Nlast night's special too?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.75,0:12:56.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure did! You too?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.30,0:12:57.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.01,0:13:00.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey guys! Are you looking for {\i1}bonheur{\i0} too?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.84,0:13:04.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go find that blue butterfly together!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.18,0:13:05.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.39,0:13:12.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I hope I find the blue butterfly\Nand it grants me eternal beauty!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.31,0:13:16.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to buy out a clothes store!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.07,0:13:19.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't decide what I want most!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.36,0:13:23.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Brown! Sally!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.41,0:13:28.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you all looking for the\Nblue butterfly of happiness too?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.29,0:13:31.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Didn't think you two would be here too!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.37,0:13:36.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I was just taking a walk,\Nand Brown asked if I wanted to come along.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.05,0:13:38.96,Default,,0,0,0,,You brought quite a lot there, Brown.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.84,0:13:42.30,Default,,0,0,0,,That can't be necessary.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.30,0:13:44.68,Default,,0,0,0,,What is this, an overseas trip?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.76,0:13:50.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, how about we all work together\Nto find the butterfly?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.39,0:13:52.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.69,0:14:00.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I think the blue butterfly\Nmight show up here!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.49,0:14:03.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Right, it'll come here to suck the nectar!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.11,0:14:06.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Blue butterfly, oh blue butterfly!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.08,0:14:09.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Papillon bleu !
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.62,0:14:12.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Blue butterfly!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.04,0:14:13.58,Default,,0,0,0,,That one's yellow...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.12,0:14:15.92,Default,,0,0,0,,No sign of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.00,0:14:19.84,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong, Jessica?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.84,0:14:21.42,Default,,0,0,0,,L-Look over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.43,0:14:29.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh? Calm down, everyone.\NTake a look.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.48,0:14:35.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Honey, that tickles... Stop it...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.52,0:14:36.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Honey who?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.52,0:14:39.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so happy...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.02,0:14:41.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Did he catch the blue butterfly\Nin his dream?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.90,0:14:44.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Where are ya,\Nblue butterfly?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.24,0:14:46.66,Default,,0,0,0,,You awake now?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.66,0:14:48.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, hey, guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.45,0:14:51.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Why were you sleeping out here, Moon?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.54,0:14:56.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Last night, I saw this special\Nand came out here to look for the blue butterfly!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.38,0:15:00.21,Default,,0,0,0,,But I forgot to bring my butterfly net.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.21,0:15:02.88,Default,,0,0,0,,...And then I got lost,\Nand now I'm starving.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.88,0:15:05.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Then I passed out here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.26,0:15:07.18,Default,,0,0,0,,So you went out without a plan?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.18,0:15:09.47,Default,,0,0,0,,That checks out.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.77,0:15:14.69,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll lend me your net, Brown?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.69,0:15:18.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks, Brown. How 'bout we go\Ncatch us some happiness?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.52,0:15:21.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright, guys!\NLet's look for the blue butterfly!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.36,0:15:25.28,Default,,0,0,0,,And no secrets! If you find it,\Nyou alert the rest of us, kapeesh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.28,0:15:29.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Like you're one to talk!\N{\i1}You{\i0} better alert {\i1}us,{\i0} ya hear?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.24,0:15:30.45,Default,,0,0,0,,There it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.45,0:15:32.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, what? Where?\NWhere is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.58,0:15:34.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh shoot.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.83,0:15:36.46,Default,,0,0,0,,What the heck, man?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.46,0:15:38.08,Default,,0,0,0,,It was there, I swear!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.46,0:15:40.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, Moon, look closer.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.79,0:15:43.80,Default,,0,0,0,,That's no blue butterfly—\Nit's an {\i1}aqua{\i0} butterfly.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.80,0:15:44.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Seriously?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.13,0:15:48.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, Brown!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.68,0:15:52.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you lend me another one?\NI'll pay you back!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.48,0:15:58.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Why thank you, Brown.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.10,0:16:01.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll remember your deeds\Nfor the rest of my weekdays.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.32,0:16:07.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Blue butterfly? Oh blue butterfly?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.82,0:16:11.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Blue butterfly! Blue butterfly!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.07,0:16:14.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Blue butterfly, blue butterfly
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.33,0:16:17.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Blue butterfly! Oh blue butterfly!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.83,0:16:21.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Papillon bleu !
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.38,0:16:25.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Where are you, blue butterfly?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.34,0:16:32.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so thirsty...\NIs there a vending machine nearby?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.60,0:16:35.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Out here in the mountains?\NDon't count on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.77,0:16:41.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Dang, Brown! You brought so many!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.40,0:16:42.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you sure we can have them?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.48,0:16:44.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks, Brown!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.94,0:16:46.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks a ton!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.74,0:16:52.20,Default,,0,0,0,,That hits the spot!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.20,0:16:53.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.62,0:16:55.62,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean go home?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.62,0:16:57.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, we kinda gotta stop here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.54,0:17:00.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Gotta stop? More like you got bored of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.29,0:17:05.88,Default,,0,0,0,,He has a point though, Cony.\NWe should really head back before the sun sets.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.88,0:17:11.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Aww, but I thought we'd get to be blessed\Nby the blue butterfly together!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.84,0:17:16.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? You'll keep searching on your own?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.10,0:17:21.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Good idea. You're far more\Nprepared than the rest of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.23,0:17:22.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.69,0:17:30.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Take care, Brown!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.04,0:17:41.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel bad making him do this alone...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.83,0:17:44.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna stay and help!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.00,0:17:46.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Cony, wait up!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.00,0:17:49.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, let her. She'd probably go\Neven if we stopped her.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.59,0:17:51.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure she'll be safe with Brown.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.88,0:17:56.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I just hope she doesn't\Ncause a burden to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.31,0:18:05.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Guess who!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.57,0:18:13.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, look at the grassland!\NWhat if the butterfly's down there?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.49,0:18:16.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.53,0:18:19.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I stayed behind so I could help you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.91,0:18:23.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, let's go check!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.17,0:18:32.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, Brown.\NWe couldn't find it at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.63,0:18:38.10,Default,,0,0,0,,You're right! We've got happiness\Nto catch for everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.10,0:18:40.85,Default,,0,0,0,,So we better find that blue butterfly!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.18,0:18:44.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I got a grass cut on my finger!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.02,0:18:49.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Brown...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.90,0:18:52.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so glad I'm with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.70,0:18:58.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Good thinking, Brown!\NNow we can get through the grass!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.49,0:19:02.41,Default,,0,0,0,,But we still can't find it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.33,0:19:07.96,Default,,0,0,0,,And now I'm hungry.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.96,0:19:12.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone else is probably having\Na yummy dinner at home about now...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.51,0:19:16.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh wow, canned dinners!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.93,0:19:18.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Great thinking, Brown!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.47,0:19:22.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's make this a feast!\NIt's gonna be so fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.27,0:19:30.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm stuffed...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.44,0:19:33.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Now I'm getting sleepy.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.41,0:19:39.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Brown, you're amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.91,0:19:41.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't mind if I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.87,0:19:42.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Hup!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.25,0:19:49.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh my, sorry. I must've eaten too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.05,0:19:55.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Now hold on. This is no camping trip.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.22,0:19:57.55,Default,,0,0,0,,We're here to find the blue butterfly!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.97,0:20:03.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Yay! We're finally out of the grassland!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.89,0:20:07.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Now I feel like having a late-night picnic!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.02,0:20:09.98,Default,,0,0,0,,The night breeze feels so good!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.45,0:20:19.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Why me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.70,0:20:26.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Head back? But I can't even walk!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.46,0:20:33.80,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll carry me?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.67,0:20:42.47,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the North Star?\NAnd it'll lead us back to Line Town?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.35,0:20:47.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Brown...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.49,0:21:00.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Blue butterfly...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.87,0:21:08.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Oh blue butterfly...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.71,0:21:13.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}of happiness...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.43,0:21:30.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Blue butterfly...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.32,0:21:40.36,Default,,0,0,0,,That was a good rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.36,0:21:41.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.91,0:21:45.83,Default,,0,0,0,,What the heck?\NWhy was I asleep on Brown?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.37,0:21:50.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh right. I sprained my ankle.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.66,0:21:54.08,Default,,0,0,0,,You must've carried me a long way, Brown.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.08,0:21:57.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Brown.\NI feel a lot better now.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.34,0:22:01.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I had a really good dream!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.59,0:22:07.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I saw the blue butterfly fluttering\Nand dancing about in the sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.39,0:22:14.98,Default,,0,0,0,,But it felt so lifelike!\NI can't help but wonder if it actually happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.94,0:22:18.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh, doesn't matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.19,0:22:23.57,Default,,0,0,0,,'Cause I realize now\NI'm happy either way!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.87,0:24:02.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Next time on {\i1}Line Town...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.87,0:24:06.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}We have a situation!\NClones of Cony came out from her nose!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.58,0:24:09.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Clones of Cony came out from her nose!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.08,0:24:12.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}You heard me.\NClones of Cony came out from her nose!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.08,0:24:14.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}That's right—clones from her nose!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.96,0:24:18.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Cony clones came from her nose!\NNose clones!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.01,0:24:19.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Tune in next time!
